'''利亞姆·波爾沃斯'''（{{lang-en|Liam Polworth}}；{{bd|1994年|10月12日}}）是一位[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]足球運動員。在場上的位置是中場。他現在效力於[[蘇超|蘇超]]球隊[[马瑟韦尔足球俱乐部|馬瑟韋爾]]，曾效力於[[因弗内斯足球俱乐部|恩華尼斯]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ictfc.com/stats/player.php?id=192|title=Profile|accessdate=27 March 2014|publisher=Inverness Caledonian Thistle F.C.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150912044735/http://ictfc.com/stats/player.php?id=192|archive-date=2015-09-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/9480349.stm|title=Inverness CT 2 - 0 Hibernian|accessdate=11 May 2011|date=11 May 2011|publisher=BBC Sport|archive-date=2019-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215074330/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/9480349.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32728510 |title=Inverness CT 2–1 Falkirk |work=BBC Sport |publisher=BBC |date=30 May 2015 |accessdate=4 June 2015 |first=Alasdair |last=Lamont |archive-date=2015-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150601220327/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32728510 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他也代表蘇格蘭U16和U17國家足球隊參賽<ref>[http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/football_player_profile.cfm?page=108&playerID=68244&squadID=17 Liam Polworth - U16 Squad]</ref><ref>[http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/football_player_profile.cfm?page=108&playerID=68244&squadID=13 Liam Polworth - U17 Squad]</ref>。
